  "description": "From the manufacturer Hilka PTJS400 400w Jig Saw Variable Speed Product Description Our powerful 450W jigsaw, a versatile tool suitable for most cutting tasks. This jigsaw features an ergonomic soft grip handle for comfortable and controlled use, along with a dust extraction facility to keep your work area clean. Its copper coiled motor ensures lasting performance, while the variable speed electronic switch provides precise control over cutting speed. The adjustable base plate allows for customized cutting angles, and the jigsaw is capable of bevel cuts from 0 to 45°. With a no-load speed of 0-3,000rpm, this jigsaw delivers efficient and reliable performance for all your cutting needs. About this item Power input: 400W Bevel cuts: 0-45° Strokes: 0-3300rpm Cable length: 2m Voltage: 230-240V ~ 50Hz Max. cutting capacity: steel 5mm, wood 55mm We take pride in being a leading name in the UK's tool and hardware industry, dedicated to offering innovative and cost-effective solutions for professionals and DIY enthusiasts alike. We offer a wide range of product, to explore our full offering visit our Amazon shop via the link in the above banner.",
